  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SF Alert 296 - Response to cholera in DRC</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project targets 24 ,000 people affected by the cholera crisis who will benefit from capacity building/mass sensitization and mobilization around the prevention of cholera and reduction of new cholera cases. There will be behavior and mentality change within the communities as well as awareness on correct use of latrines and drinking water.</narrative>
  </description>
